    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Rare find alert! This vehicle is in truly mint condition \u2014 and it shows from every angle. The exterior paint is flawless, gleaming like it just rolled off the showroom floor with zero scratches, chips, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is immaculate: fresh, clean upholstery, spotless surfaces, and everything functioning exactly as it should. Under the hood, you'll find an engine that runs beautifully and has been well cared for throughout its life. If you've been searching for a vehicle that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is your chance. Don't miss out \u2014 mint-condition finds like this don't last long!",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly option or a project car? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it runs but shows significant wear and will need some attention and repairs to get it back in top shape. It's a great opportunity for a handy buyer or someone who needs basic transportation and doesn't mind putting in a little work. Priced honestly at $5,500 \u2014 what you see is what you get, no surprises!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a reliable, well-maintained option for buyers seeking dependable transportation at a reasonable price. The exterior shows normal signs of use, including some minor scratches and light surface wear consistent with everyday driving, but no significant dents or structural damage. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on the seats and trim that you'd expect from a regularly used vehicle. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and all major systems are in working order. There may be minor maintenance items to address down the road, as is typical for a vehicle of this age and use, but nothing that would compromise day-to-day reliability. This is a solid, honest buy for someone who wants a good-running car without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 31000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and that designation is fully earned. The exterior paint is absolutely pristine \u2014 a deep, rich gloss with zero scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim pieces, chrome accents, and glass surfaces are immaculate. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor \u2014 the upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are free of wear or staining, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, steering, transmission \u2014 perform flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that genuinely requires nothing. No repairs, no reconditioning, no surprises \u2014 just a car in exceptional, move-in-ready condition.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you visit. The exterior shows visible wear beyond typical minor scratches \u2014 expect some dents, fading paint, and surface rust in spots that are noticeable but not structurally concerning. The interior has seen regular use, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on trim panels, and general signs of age throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 there could be minor maintenance items or aging components that a new owner should budget for. This is not a pristine vehicle, but it is priced accordingly and represents a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who doesn't need perfection. A pre-purchase inspection is welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
