      "description": "Affordable and ready to roll! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it's a solid, functional car that gets the job done dependably. The exterior shows visible signs of wear including some scratches and minor dents consistent with its age and use, and the interior has noticeable wear on the seats and surfaces. Mechanically, it runs and drives, making it a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer looking for everyday transportation. A great opportunity to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank! \ud83d\udcaa",
